3. Engage healthcare valuation expert (AVA, ASA) for SNF licenses ($60K-$100K)
4. Engage business valuation expert (ASA, CFA, ABV) for managed care contracts and non-compete agreements ($70K-$120K)
5. Provide appraisers with financial data, facility information, payor contracts, executive employment agreements
6. Review draft appraisal reports and negotiate final allocation with Golden Gate Capital

**Expected Outcome:** Comprehensive appraisal package supporting $425M allocation across Class I-VII; written allocation agreement executed as exhibit to Asset Purchase Agreement.

